：Scott Dudelson 和 Arnold Jerocki，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Kanye-West.-Credit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Kanye-West.-Credit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Kanye-West.-Credit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Kanye-West.-Credit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Kanye-West.-Credit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Kanye-West.-Credit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在坎耶·韦斯特<a href="/artists/kanye-west">(Kanye West)</a>未经许可采样了奥斯本的一首曲目后，<a href="/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本 (</a> Ozzy Osbourne) 公开表示要与坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West) 对抗。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">Kanye West 和 Ty Dolla $ign – “Vultures 1”评论：深陷厌女症</a></strong></li></ul><p>两人之间的冲突于本月早些时候爆发，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>主唱在社交媒体上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">指责说唱歌手未经许可采样了他的一首歌曲</a>。</p><p>奥斯本得知韦斯特已将黑色安息日歌曲“钢铁侠”的样本循环到他的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">“秃鹫”</a>中。据报道，韦斯特于 2 月 8 日在芝加哥联合中心举行的与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-$ign">Ty Dolla $ign</a>一起宣传新专辑的活动中播放了这段视频。</p><p>作为对这种用法的回应，这位金属偶像猛烈抨击了 West，他在 Instagram 上分享了一篇长篇帖子， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">称这位说唱歌手是“反犹太分子”</a> 。</p><p>他写道，韦斯特“请求允许试听 1983 年美国音乐节现场表演《战猪》的一段无声乐片段”，但随后“被拒绝，因为他是一名反犹太主义者，给许多人带来了难以言喻的心痛”。该帖子后来被修改为歌曲“钢铁侠”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3xwQ_QxOkw/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C